{"tid":1546063,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[絲打受害]黑警逼癲人 絲打唔敢再發夢","createTime":"2019-09-06T06:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T09:15:05.000Z","uid":264327,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e96c5e081dcaa523e3156e96872b27af950abeb6","tid":1546063,"uid":264327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/axLwCni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxLwCni.jpg&h=6863956a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家一定要知，絲打們既心路歷程，如果唔係真係可能會死人。<br />\n<br />\n碌碌下FB俾我見到有人share呢篇drcard文，呢個絲打怕影響士氣唔喺呢度po <br />\n原諒我忍唔住share左過黎<br />\n<br />\n見到都真係好L嬲同sad<br />\n日日望到電視d黑警係度對d絲打出手<br />\n絲打們原來係承受咁大壓力 <br />\n係度要同各位絲打講一句：辛苦曬！<br />\n<br />\n你地完全顛覆左我對港女既想像<br />\n有時仲好OP，特別係前兩日果位保護心臟病人既救護<br />\n如果無左你地我地都唔知點算！<br />\n<br />\n但係我都要呼籲，如果你地有任何人好似篇文咁講有影響到自己情緒，唔好再勉強自己出去發夢。<br />\n巴打絲打都係！<br />\n無人會怪你地，休息夠我地再一齊努力！<br />\n文宣、媒體仲需要你地既力量！<br />\n不割席、不分化、不篤灰。<br />\n<br />\nP.S有無account都過去關心下呢位絲打啦<br />\n多個網站睇下 update 資訊都無壞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcard.tw/f/hkmacdaily/p/231996348-%E5%B0%8D%E5%94%94%E4%BD%8F...%E6%AF%94%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%B4%8F%E5%B7%A6%E6%AC%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%8E%9F%E8%AB%92%E6%88%91%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%94%94%E6%95%A2%E5%86%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%A4%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcard.tw%2Ff%2Fhkmacdaily%2Fp%2F231996348-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%2594%2594%25E4%25BD%258F...%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E8%25B4%258F%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E6%25AC%25A1%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%258E%259F%25E8%25AB%2592%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2594%2594%25E6%2595%25A2%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25A4%25A2&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=3aa94c97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcard.tw/f/hkmacdaily/p/231996348-%E5%B0%8D%E5%94%94%E4%BD%8F...%E6%AF%94%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%B4%8F%E5%B7%A6%E6%AC%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%8E%9F%E8%AB%92%E6%88%91%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%94%94%E6%95%A2%E5%86%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%A4%A2</a>"},{"pid":"abca659506dc0a813a3212ccf851065b11128a6d","tid":1546063,"uid":76702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:40:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ae5eab23cc23ea77d220294e41404867606ffdd","tid":1546063,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:41:35.000Z","msg":"手足最重要 有需要就退落黎休息 冇人會怪你！"},{"pid":"5d7e10c6fed6de6ca27fb067760d84433d0b915b","tid":1546063,"uid":45324,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:41:36.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"29bdff8ddd4dc37dde83a66c8ebbb2dd5a1efc0c","tid":1546063,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:43:06.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3dd01fa73ed21b510d273661d3320589e41f0ffc","tid":1546063,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:43:26.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=c6f901fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"d2156e993274aeaf42abbd6ccd23070ae4c4ad45","tid":1546063,"uid":93350,"like":3,"dis